    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving peak. Powered by the S54 3.2L straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS, it delivers linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical maintenance is up to date, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS refresh to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. While showing minor cosmetic wear typical of its vintage, the drivetrain and suspension are dialed in for immediate performance. A true driver\u2019s spec ready for the canyons.",
