    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained 2019 Audi Q5 Premium Plus offers a perfect balance of luxury and performance. Finished in a deep Moonlight Blue Metallic, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, though careful inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway commuting. Inside, the Atlas Beige leather interior remains supple and free of tears or odors, having been kept in a smoke-free environment. All technological features, including the Virtual Cockpit and panoramic sunroof, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it comes with a complete portfolio of service records from the local dealership, including a recent oil service and a fresh set of brake pads installed last month. The tires show significant remaining tread, ensuring a smooth, quiet ride for the next owner. This is a reliable, turn-key luxury SUV that has been cared for with pride.",
