      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This driver-spec example features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the chassis handles the 8,000 RPM redline with precision. The suspension remains tight with upgraded bushings and dampers, providing excellent lateral grip and feedback. While exhibiting minor aesthetic patina, its performance envelope is fully intact, offering an unadulterated analog driving experience for the serious enthusiast.",
